<p><a href="https://www.legislation.gov.au/Series/C2004A00491" title="A New Tax System (Family Assistance) (Administration) Act 1999">FA(Admin)Act</a> section 67FB Notice of change of circumstances: individuals</p>
<p><a href="https://www.legislation.gov.au/Series/F2017L01464" title="Child Care Subsidy Minister's Rules 2017">CCSMinRules</a> section 8A Purpose of prescribing classes of children in the Division, section 8B Children 13 years or under who are attending secondary school who do not have a prescribed disability or prescribed medical condition, section 8C Children who have a prescribed disability or prescribed medical condition, section 8D Conditions in relation to the classes of children prescribed in sections 8B and 8C</p>
<p><strong>Policy reference:</strong> FA Guide <a href="../family-assistance-guide/5/2/1.1">5.2.1</a> Change of circumstances, <a href="../family-assistance-guide/2/6/1">2.6.1</a> CCS eligibility, <a href="../family-assistance-guide/2/6/3.1">2.6.3</a> CCS eligibility - attending secondary school</p>
</div>
